                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, H</hi> 43). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "June</hi>, 1853; <hi rend="italic">Convicted of larceny, from the person, and 
Transported for Ten Years</hi>")—I was present at that conviction—Clarke is the person.</p>
               <p>
